25")) (item nil (title nil "突然想到标题栏实际上可以当标签页栏来使用") (dc:creator nil "@LdBeth 好船") (description nil " <p>说笑。这个虽然是 vim 特色功能<br>不过的确已经有 Emacs Tabbar 插件了。</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/topic/2702/4") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 12:22:22 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11224")) (item nil (title nil "突然想到标题栏实际上可以当标签页栏来使用") (dc:creator nil "@lululau lululau") (description nil " <p>是吗，还有这说法吗</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/topic/2702/3") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 12:17:01 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11222")) (item nil (title nil "突然想到标题栏实际上可以当标签页栏来使用") (dc:creator nil "@LdBeth 好船") (description nil " <p>标签页是邪教……</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/topic/2702/2") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 11:41:44 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11221")) (item nil (title nil "突然想到标题栏实际上可以当标签页栏来使用") (dc:creator nil "@lululau lululau") (description nil " <p>比如我用 Spacemacs 的 Project Layout，</p><p>然后把 title format 定义成：</p><p></p><pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">(defun lx/layout-format-name (name pos)
  \"Format the layout name given by NAME for display in mode-line.\"
  (let* ((layout-name (if (file-directory-p name)
                          (file-name-nondirectory (directory-file-name name))
                        name))
         (string-name (format \"%s\" layout-name))
         (current (equal name (spacemacs//current-layout-name)))
         (caption (concat (number-to-string (if (eq 9 pos) 0 (1+ pos)))
                          \". \" string-name)))
    (if current
        (propertize (concat \"❰❰ \" caption \" ❱❱\") 'face 'warning)
      caption)))


(defun lx/layouts-for-title-bar ()
  \"Return a one liner string containing all the layout names.\"
  (let* ((persp-list (or (persp-names-current-frame-fast-ordered)
                         (list persp-nil-name)))
         (formatted-persp-list
          (concat \" \"
                  (mapconcat (lambda (persp)
                               (lx/layout-format-name
                                persp (position persp persp-list)))
                             persp-list \"          \"))))
    formatted-persp-list))

(setq frame-title-format '(:eval (lx/layouts-for-title-bar))))</code></pre><p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a data-download-href=\"https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/cdd021ac4405392cb2a4b87e49f75667dd647887\" href=\"https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cdd021ac4405392cb2a4b87e49f75667dd647887.png\" class=\"lightbox\" title=\"QQ20170415-190257@2x.png\"><img src=\"https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cdd021ac4405392cb2a4b87e49f75667dd647887_1_690x418.png\" width=\"690\" height=\"418\"><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">QQ20170415-190257@2x.png</span><span class=\"informations\">2560x1554 389 KB</span><span class=\"expand\"></span></div></a></div></p><p>然后把 <code>s-number</code> 绑定到切换 persp：</p><p></p><pre><code class=\"lang-lisp\">(global-set-key (kbd \"s-0\") 'spacemacs/persp-switch-to-0)
(global-set-key (kbd \"s-1\") 'spacemacs/persp-switch-to-1)
... ...</code></pre> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/topic/2702/1") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 11:07:35 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11220")) (item nil (title nil "如何设置打开.scala文件时默认启动scala-mode?") (dc:creator nil "@lululau lululau") (description nil " <p>不对, Spacemacs 的 scala layer 是关联了 <code>.scala</code> 后缀的</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/scala-scala-mode/2700/3") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 08:55:15 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11219")) (item nil (title nil "如何设置打开.scala文件时默认启动scala-mode?") (dc:creator nil "@lululau lululau") (description nil " <p>搜 auto-mode-alist，玩 Emacs 就不要做伸手党</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/scala-scala-mode/2700/2") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 08:53:05 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11218")) (item nil (title nil "如何设置打开.scala文件时默认启动scala-mode?") (dc:creator nil "@oshua Night Eternal") (description nil " <p>在spacemacs的那个位置设置，当打开.scala文件时默认启动scala-mode?</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/scala-scala-mode/2700/1") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 07:58:39 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11216")) (item nil (title nil "如何在单位内网部署一个 ELPA 镜像") (dc:creator nil "@twlz0ne Twlz0ne") (description nil " <p>如果不要求镜像整个仓库，可以看看陈斌的 <a href=\"https://github.com/redguardtoo/elpa-mirror\">https://github.com/redguardtoo/elpa-mirror</a></p><blockquote><p>Create local Emacs package repository.</p><p><b>Only installed packages</b> will be included in the repository.</p></blockquote> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/elpa/2697/4") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 04:20:08 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11215")) (item nil (title nil "如何在单位内网部署一个 ELPA 镜像") (dc:creator nil "@gulei gulei") (description nil " <p>谢了，我尝试一哈~</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/elpa/2697/3") (pubDate nil "Sat, 15 Apr 2017 02:58:26 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-c