   (replace-regexp-in-string \"\\n+\" \"\\n\"
      (replace-regexp-in-string \"\\n{1}\" \" \" string)))</code></pre><p>不是很懂正则，不知道有没有bug……</p><p>好吧……其实这个和你的要求有出入，会把连续多个换行变成一个换行，而不是只变第一个。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/gamesun/archive/2013/02/05/2893382.html\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnblogs.com/gamesun/archive/2013/02/05/2893382.html</a></p><blockquote><p>在GNU Emacs的正式发行版中，正则表达式对<a href=\"http://www.regular-expressions.info/lookaround.html\">环视</a>是不支持的......</p></blockquote><p>所以似乎</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"2689\"><div class=\"title\"><div class=\"quote-controls\"></div><img alt=\" \" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://emacs-china.org/user_avatar/emacs-china.org/ziyuanjun/40/910_1.png\" class=\"avatar\">ziyuanjun:</div><blockquote><ol><li>当连续多个回车时，只将一个回车替换为空格，其余回车保留</li></ol></blockquote></aside><p>是不太好做的。</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/emacs-google/2689/5") (pubDate nil "Fri, 14 Apr 2017 03:44:40 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11186")) (item nil (title nil "[已解决] 如何将 SPC-o 映射或者说 key-translation-map 到 C-c 上") (dc:creator nil "@Voleking Voleking") (description nil " <p>没有，能回答已经十分感谢了。<br>其实我自己应该可以反映过来，感觉不多学点 emacs-lisp 配置起来果然好浪费时间orz</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/spc-o-key-translation-map-c-c/2692/7") (pubDate nil "Fri, 14 Apr 2017 03:41:31 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11185")) (item nil (title nil "[已解决] 如何将 SPC-o 映射或者说 key-translation-map 到 C-c 上") (dc:creator nil "@LdBeth 好船") (description nil " <p>不好意思一开始把标题意思理解反了。</p> ") (link nil "https://emacs-china.org/t/spc-o-key-translation-map-c-c/2692/6") (pubDate nil "Fri, 14 Apr 2017 03:33:40 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "emacs-china.org-post-11183")))) ("buffer末尾显示在window的位置，如何修改？" "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a data-download-href=\"https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/1359d69a432940d75ead0d6590866d2eccb35845\" href=\"https://emacs-china.org/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1359d69a432940d75e